# =============================================================================
# INDEX {{{
# =============================================================================

color tree blue black
color index_number green black

# Status flags
color index yellow black ~N # New
color index green black ~Q # Replied
color index red black ~D # Deleted
color index magenta black ~F # Flagged
color index cyan black ~T # Tagged
color index blue black ~v # Collapsed

# }}}
# =============================================================================
